## üì± Responsive Implementation

### Recommended Breakpoint Strategy

For responsive scaling between mobile ‚Üí laptop ‚Üí desktop:

```html
<!-- Display L: Scales from mobile to laptop to desktop -->
<h1
  class="font-['Montserrat'] text-[40px] sm:text-[56px] md:text-[72px] xl:text-[96px] font-bold leading-none uppercase text-[#083D45]"
>
  Responsive Display L
</h1>
```

### Tailwind Breakpoint Reference

- `sm:` - 640px (mobile landscape / small tablet)
- `md:` - 768px (tablet)
- `lg:` - 1024px (laptop) ‚Üê **Laptop starts here**
- `xl:` - 1280px (desktop)
- `2xl:` - 1536px (large desktop)

